--- conversations ---

/init                   # read over files in project to understand it, produces CLAUDE.md
/rename [session]       # rename a session
/export [file].md       # export full conversation to a file
/resume                 # open session picker
/history                # list all commands run across sessions

--- context ---

<esc> <esc>             # return to a previous point in convo, forget recent messages
/compact                # after claude has learned something useful and you want to carry it forward
/clear                  # remove context and conversation history

